<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>الْإِلْغَازِ،<span style="color:#006d98"> كَقَوْلِهِ:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>عَافَتِ الْمَاءَ فِي الشِّتَاءِ فَقُلَّنَا ... بَرِّدِيهِ تُصَادِفِيهِ سَخِينَا<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span style="color:#006d98">أَيْ:</span> بَلْ رِدِيهِ، أَمْرٌ مِنَ الْوُرُودِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وَكَقَوْلِهِ:</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>لَمَّا رَأَيْتُ أَبَا يَزِيدَ مُقَاتِلًا ... أَدَعَ الْقِتَالَ وَأَشْهَدَ الْهَيْجَاءَ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>أَيْ لَنْ أَدَعَ الْقِتَالَ مَا رَأَيْتُ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>وَهُنَاكَ تَفْصِيلٌ فِي وَصْلِ <span style="color:#008000">(مِنْ)</span> و <span style="color:#008000">(مَا)</span> و <span style="color:#008000">(لَا)</span> بِمَا قَبْلَهَا.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>- وَصْلُ <span style="color:#008000">(مَنْ)</span> بِمَا قَبْلَهَا -<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>تُوصَلُ <span style="color:#008000">(مِنْ)</span> الْاِسْتِفْهَامِيَّةُ وَالْمَوْصُولَةُ بِمَنْ، وَعَنْ، وَفِي،<span style="color:#006d98"> نَحْوُ:</span> مِمَّنْ عَلِمْتَ هَذَا؟ عَمَّنْ تَسْأَل؟<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>